column55: I would not recommend USS to locals who have the capacity/intend to travel to other countries and non-locals. This is because other theme parks, such as USJ (which has the attractions that USS has and more), have more facilities and ride variety to provide a more enjoyable experience. However, to those who are unable to travel overseas but want to experience a theme park, I would recommend it to them as it would be a fun activity given Singaporeâ€™s limited attractions.
